the "How have you been?" kind of talking.

31
00:01:28,033 --> 00:01:31,753
More of the "Pierce its eye
with something sharp" kind of talking.

32
00:01:31,753 --> 00:01:35,903
- l'm thinking l should call her.
- l don't want you to get your hopes up.

33
00:01:35,913 --> 00:01:37,713
