Help wronged women punish evil men.

161
00:15:36,393 --> 00:15:39,243
- Vengeance.
- But only to those who deserve it.

162
00:15:39,473 --> 00:15:43,223
- They all deserve it.
- That's where l was going with that, yeah.

163
