so much blood.

177
00:16:40,313 --> 00:16:43,193
l'd forgotten the damage
a Crimslaw demon could do.

178
00:16:43,193 --> 00:16:47,893
Oh, tell me about it. They can be feisty
little guys - and impossible to house-train.

179
00:16:47,953 --> 00:16:50,153
